{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "本章中，俞六显露出与粗朴外表完全不同的精密才干：地道、马车、诱敌和藏身处都由他统筹安排。他带众人进入一座尚未入住的华屋过夜，以避开无十三对连夜赶路的判断。夜深后，谢玉宝与大婉同室而眠，旧日被点穴、验身的羞辱重新爆发为怨恨。她封住大婉穴道，诱马如龙去看草席下的人，声称要以同样方式报复大婉；然而马如龙掀开草席时，下面竟不是大婉，而是那个又聋又哑又驼又老的残废老人，局势转入更诡异危险的夜局。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "你从来没有在江湖中走动？你都在做些什么事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "什么事我都做，只不过通常我都在替别人盖房子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "你是个泥水匠？还是木匠？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "泥水匠我也做，木工我也做，只不过通常我都是在打样子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "现在我才知道，你五哥为什么要特地请你来挖洞了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "要挖那么样一条地道，一定比盖房子还难。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那条地道也不是我一个人能挖得出来的，刚才坐另外三辆马车走的人，全都是我的帮手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "他们当然都是你五哥派来的，都是丐帮的子弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "他们也不是丐帮子弟，他们都是帮我盖房子的人，所以他们也会挖洞。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "这件事全是你计划的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "我五哥既然要我替他来做这件事，我当然要替他办好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "你五哥呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "他把这件事交给我，自己就什么都不管了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "text": "如果我也有你这么一个兄弟，我也会像俞五一样，什么都不必操心了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "各位请下车。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "下车？下车干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "今天晚上，我们就留在这里！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "为什么要留在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "因为无十三一定也认为我们会连夜赶路的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "这是个好主意！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "这是我最近替人盖的一栋房子，屋主是位已退隐致仕的高官，要等到下个月中才会搬进来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "刚才开门的人是谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_zhong_ren",
      "text": "也是帮我盖房子的人，我保证他绝不会泄漏我们的秘密。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你睡着了没有？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你为什么睡不着？你心里在想些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我什么都没有想，我只想好好的睡一觉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你用不着骗我，我知道你心里在想什么。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你在想马如龙，我知道你很喜欢他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你为什么睡不着？你心里也在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我也跟你一样，我也在想马如龙，这几个月来，他每天晚上都跟我睡在一间屋子里，每天晚上我都可以听见他的呼吸声，现在我怎么会不想他？怎么能睡得着？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我没有姐妹，我这一辈子最接近的人就是你，我从来都没有想到你会害我，所以那天你忽然出手点住我的穴道时，我实在吃了一惊。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "现在我虽然已经明白你那么做是一番好意，但当时却真的吃了一惊！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "如果那时候我已经完全晕迷反倒好些，可惜我居然还很清醒，你对我做的每件事，我全都知道，那些事我这一辈子都忘不了的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你把我带到那个衙门里去，把我关在一间小房子里，脱光我的衣服，让我躺在一张又冷又硬的木板床上，还带了一个男人来看我的身子，每件事我都知道。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "那时候我以为你已经晕过去了，所以……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你知不知道那时候我心里是什么感觉？你知不知道一个女孩子第一次被男人看的时候，心里是什么感觉？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你当然不会知道，因为你还没有被人脱光衣服，还没有被男人看过。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可是我保证你很快就会知道了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "现在你很快就会知道那时候我心里是什么感觉了，因为我也要用你对付我的法子来对付你，也要让马如龙来看看你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我要带你去看样东西，我保证，你定会喜欢看的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你把草席掀起来看看，先看这一头，再看那一头。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我本来以为你不会这么吃惊的，因为你也应该想得到，我一定会报复。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你要报复的是谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "当然是大婉，以前她怎么样对我，现在我就要怎么样对她。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "以前她怎么对你，现在你就要怎么对她。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你是不是也把她的穴道点住？是不是把她放在这张草席下面了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    }
  ],
